  <abstract>This is a guide for parents on how to be the best advocates for their children. The booklet guides parents on how to speak out and act on behalf of children with tips on how to manage advocacy, a listing of national child advocacy organizations that can be of assistance, a listing of public policy and advocacy offices of religious groups, and state-level child advocacy organizations.</abstract>
